$$
\vec{r}_{O_2} = OA + \frac{1}{2}AB
$$

动能

$$
\begin{align*}
T &amp;= \frac{1}{2} m_1 \dot{\vec{r}}_{O_2}^2 + \frac{1}{2} J \dot{\theta}_2^2 \\
 &amp;= \frac{m}{2} L_1^2 \dot{\theta}_1^2 
 + \frac{m}{6} L_2^2 \dot{\theta}_2^2 
 + \frac{m}{2} L_1 L_2 \dot{\theta}_1 \dot{\theta}_2 \cos \left( \theta_2 - \theta_1 \right)
\end{align*}
$$

势能

$$
\begin{align*}
V &amp;= mg \left( L_1 \left( 1 - \cos \theta_1 \right) + \frac{1}{2} L_2 \left( 1 - \cos \theta_2 \right) \right) \\
 &amp;= mg \left( L_1 + \frac{1}{2} L_2 \right) - mg L_1 \cos \theta_1 - \frac{1}{2} mg L_2 \cos \theta_2
\end{align*}
$$

代入Lagrange方程:

$$
\begin{cases}
m L_1^2 \ddot{\theta}_1 + \frac{m}{2} L_1 L_2 \ddot{\theta}_2 \cos \left( \theta_2 - \theta_1 \right) + \frac{m}{2} L_1 L_2 \dot{\theta}_2 \left( \dot{\theta}_2 - \dot{\theta}_1 \right) \sin \left( \theta_2 - \theta_1 \right) - \frac{m}{2} L_1 L_2 \dot{\theta}_1 \dot{\theta}_2 \sin \left( \theta_2 - \theta_1 \right) + mg L_1 \sin \theta_1 &amp;= 0\\
\frac{m}{3} L_2^2 \ddot{\theta}_2 + \frac{m}{2} L_1 L_2 \ddot{\theta}_1 \cos \left( \theta_2 - \theta_1 \right) - \frac{m}{2} L_1 L_2 \dot{\theta}_1 \left( \dot{\theta}_2 - \dot{\theta}_1 \right) \sin \left( \theta_2 - \theta_1 \right) + \frac{m}{2} L_1 L_2 \dot{\theta}_1 \dot{\theta}_2 \sin \left( \theta_2 - \theta_1 \right) + \frac{1}{2} mg L_2 \sin \theta_2 &amp;= 0
\end{cases}
$$

线性化

$$\sin \theta \approx \theta, \cos \theta \approx 1, \dot \theta^2 \approx 0$$

则有

$$
\begin{cases}
m L_1^2 \ddot{\theta}_1 + \frac{1}{2} m L_1 L_2 \ddot{\theta}_2 + mg L_1 \theta_1 &amp;= 0 \\
\frac{1}{2} m L_1 L_2 \ddot{\theta}_1 + \frac{1}{3} m L_2^2 \ddot{\theta}_2 + \frac{1}{2} mg L_2 \theta_2 &amp;= 0
\end{cases}
$$

写出矩阵形式

$$
\begin{pmatrix}
mL_1^2 &amp; \frac{m}{2} L_1 L_2 \\
\frac{m}{2} L_1 L_2 &amp; \frac{m}{3} L_2^2
\end{pmatrix}
\begin{pmatrix}
\ddot{\theta}_1 \\
\ddot{\theta}_2
\end{pmatrix} + 
\begin{pmatrix}
mgL_1 &amp; 0 \\
0 &amp; \frac{1}{2} mgL_2
\end{pmatrix}
\begin{pmatrix}
\theta_1 \\
\theta_2
\end{pmatrix} = 
\begin{pmatrix}
0 \\
0
\end{pmatrix}
$$"><p>建立坐标如图</p><p></p><div class="MathJax" display="block" style="text-align:center;"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="17.874ex" height="4.588ex" role="img" focusable="false" $$
\begin{pmatrix}
L &amp; \frac{1}{2} L \\
\frac{1}{2} L &amp; \frac{1}{3} L
\end{pmatrix}
\begin{pmatrix}
\ddot{\theta}_1 \\
\ddot{\theta}_2
\end{pmatrix} + 
\begin{pmatrix}
g &amp; 0 \\
0 &amp; \frac{1}{2} g
\end{pmatrix}
\begin{pmatrix}
\theta_1 \\
\theta_2
\end{pmatrix} = 
\begin{pmatrix}
0 \\
0
\end{pmatrix}
$$

则特征多项式

$$
\begin{align*}
\left| K - \lambda M \right| &amp;= \begin{vmatrix}
g - \lambda L &amp; - \frac{\lambda}{2} L \\
-\frac{\lambda}{2} L &amp; \frac{1}{2} g - \frac{\lambda}{3} L
\end{vmatrix} \\
&amp;= \frac{1}{12} \lambda^2 L^2 - \frac{5}{6} \lambda g L + \frac{1}{2} g^2 \\
&amp;= 0
\end{align*}
$$

$${\lambda _{1,2}} = \left( {5 \mp \sqrt {19} } \right)\frac{g}{L}$$

$${\omega _{1,2}} = \sqrt {\left( {5 \mp \sqrt {19} } \right)\frac{g}{L}}$$

 0.89315, &amp;1

div.data-content:
建立坐标如图

$$
\vec{r}_{O_2} = OA + \frac{1}{2}AB
$$

动能

$$
\begin{align*}
T &= \frac{1}{2} m_1 \dot{\vec{r}}_{O_2}^2 + \frac{1}{2} J \dot{\theta}_2^2 \\
&= \frac{m}{2} L_1^2 \dot{\theta}_1^2
+ \frac{m}{6} L_2^2 \dot{\theta}_2^2
+ \frac{m}{2} L_1 L_2 \dot{\theta}_1 \dot{\theta}_2 \cos \left( \theta_2 - \theta_1 \right)
\end{align*}
$$

势能

$$
\begin{align*}
V &= mg \left( L_1 \left( 1 - \cos \theta_1 \right) + \frac{1}{2} L_2 \left( 1 - \cos \theta_2 \right) \right) \\
&= mg \left( L_1 + \frac{1}{2} L_2 \right) - mg L_1 \cos \theta_1 - \frac{1}{2} mg L_2 \cos \theta_2
\end{align*}
$$

代入Lagrange方程:

$$
\begin{cases}
m L_1^2 \ddot{\theta}_1 + \frac{m}{2} L_1 L_2 \ddot{\theta}_2 \cos \left( \theta_2 - \theta_1 \right) + \frac{m}{2} L_1 L_2 \dot{\theta}_2 \left( \dot{\theta}_2 - \dot{\theta}_1 \right) \sin \left( \theta_2 - \theta_1 \right) - \frac{m}{2} L_1 L_2 \dot{\theta}_1 \dot{\theta}_2 \sin \left( \theta_2 - \theta_1 \right) + mg L_1 \sin \theta_1 &= 0\\
\frac{m}{3} L_2^2 \ddot{\theta}_2 + \frac{m}{2} L_1 L_2 \ddot{\theta}_1 \cos \left( \theta_2 - \theta_1 \right) - \frac{m}{2} L_1 L_2 \dot{\theta}_1 \left( \dot{\theta}_2 - \dot{\theta}_1 \right) \sin \left( \theta_2 - \theta_1 \right) + \frac{m}{2} L_1 L_2 \dot{\theta}_1 \dot{\theta}_2 \sin \left( \theta_2 - \theta_1 \right) + \frac{1}{2} mg L_2 \sin \theta_2 &= 0
\end{cases}
$$

线性化

$$\sin \theta \approx \theta, \cos \theta \approx 1, \dot \theta^2 \approx 0$$

则有

$$
\begin{cases}
m L_1^2 \ddot{\theta}_1 + \frac{1}{2} m L_1 L_2 \ddot{\theta}_2 + mg L_1 \theta_1 &= 0 \\
\frac{1}{2} m L_1 L_2 \ddot{\theta}_1 + \frac{1}{3} m L_2^2 \ddot{\theta}_2 + \frac{1}{2} mg L_2 \theta_2 &= 0
\end{cases}
$$

写出矩阵形式

$$
\begin{pmatrix}
mL_1^2 & \frac{m}{2} L_1 L_2 \\
\frac{m}{2} L_1 L_2 & \frac{m}{3} L_2^2
\end{pmatrix}
\begin{pmatrix}
\ddot{\theta}_1 \\
\ddot{\theta}_2
\end{pmatrix} +
\begin{pmatrix}
mgL_1 & 0 \\
0 & \frac{1}{2} mgL_2
\end{pmatrix}
\begin{pmatrix}
\theta_1 \\
\theta_2
\end{pmatrix} =
\begin{pmatrix}
0 \\
0
\end{pmatrix}
$$

div.data-content:
代入$L_1 = L_2 = L$

$$
\begin{pmatrix}
L & \frac{1}{2} L \\
\frac{1}{2} L & \frac{1}{3} L
\end{pmatrix}
\begin{pmatrix}
\ddot{\theta}_1 \\
\ddot{\theta}_2
\end{pmatrix} +
\begin{pmatrix}
g & 0 \\
0 & \frac{1}{2} g
\end{pmatrix}
\begin{pmatrix}
\theta_1 \\
\theta_2
\end{pmatrix} =
\begin{pmatrix}
0 \\
0
\end{pmatrix}
$$

则特征多项式

$$
\begin{align*}
\left| K - \lambda M \right| &= \begin{vmatrix}
g - \lambda L & - \frac{\lambda}{2} L \\
-\frac{\lambda}{2} L & \frac{1}{2} g - \frac{\lambda}{3} L
\end{vmatrix} \\
&= \frac{1}{12} \lambda^2 L^2 - \frac{5}{6} \lambda g L + \frac{1}{2} g^2 \\
&= 0
\end{align*}
$$

得特征值

$${\lambda _{1,2}} = \left( {5 \mp \sqrt {19} } \right)\frac{g}{L}$$

$${\omega _{1,2}} = \sqrt {\left( {5 \mp \sqrt {19} } \right)\frac{g}{L}}$$

得特征向量

$$
\begin{cases}
u_1 &= c_1 \begin{pmatrix}
0.89315, &1
\end{pmatrix} \\
u_2 &= c_2 \begin{pmatrix}
-0.559816, &1
\end{pmatrix} \\
\end{cases}
$$
